name: Jetpack Survival
description:
Survive as long as possible while avoiding walls of death and orbs of doom... Jk :P

Since no leaderboards, screenshot your score and comment it below!!

Still in development.

Can use "spacebar" to go and Left and Right arrow keys to change directions.

or if on phone can use the touch screen controls (only 1 can be used at a time, trying to fix it)
